### âœ… 3. Prepare Your `.env` (Optional for OpenAI)

Create a `.env` file in the root folder with:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here
```

This enables advanced AI features (GPT-powered analysis).

### âœ… 4. Add Your CSV File

